{"tid":119380,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"(番梘, Mask) Lush 真係好用！","createTime":"2017-02-13T16:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T03:14:37.000Z","uid":58951,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"970fd180ac96a1a1c2c34553a33e6af2ef6a576b","tid":119380,"uid":58951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T16:42:43.000Z","msg":"用過Lush 嘅2款洗頭梘<br />\n貪佢天然得黎又夠香<br />\n<br />\n用過 頭皮拜拜 同埋 摩洛哥油 兩款<br />\n頭皮拜拜：用完少左頭皮，不過隔日洗頭仍會痕<br />\n<br />\n依家用 摩洛哥油梘：<br />\n玖瑰味整到廁所勁香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n潤得黎唔會笠，<br />\n第二日都無頭痕，好舒服，<br />\n甩頭髮都少左<br />\n<br />\n我會先會iherb 買嘅grandpa pine tar soap 洗第一次，<br />\n之後先用lush 梘，易啲起泡，好似慳啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n護髮素就啱啱由Essential 轉左做Nature Gate,<br />\n不含矽嗰啲，無咁滑潺潺，清爽舒服又順到頭髮<br />\n<br />\n之前電染到好毛躁，<br />\n吹完頭會用椰子油再潤下佢，就好好多<br />\n<br />\n黎緊想試其他手工皀店嘅護髮素<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同埋開post 重點係：<br />\nLush UK Site 價錢平香港一半<br />\n但運費要&pound;9<br />\n有無人一齊買，夾運費？</span><br />\n<br />\n英磅匯率加credit card 手續費計返大約x10<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://uk.lush.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuk.lush.com%2F&d=%2BD6XGwqev%2FlZKpArKwvoHdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=7701e49a\" target=\"_blank\">https://uk.lush.com/</a>"},{"pid":"97324eca51ad4c62a985b41eb3a65265ee2b6415","tid":119380,"uid":58951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T16:44:36.000Z","msg":"另外用過佢嘅fresh mask<br />\nKiwi fruit 同blueberry <br />\n<br />\nKiwi 用白左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBlueberry 好滋潤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45eeb0299a1e4c07e6ac23142e544a6a9d817f14","tid":119380,"uid":75359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T16:47:50.000Z","msg":"鐘意藍色檸檬mask ,成屋都lush<br />\n利伸：上年年尾quit左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid