Oil<br />\nViolet Leaf Absolute<br />\nRose Absolute<br />\nBergamot Oil<br />\nCananga Oil<br />\n*Limonene<br />\n*Linalool<br />\n*Citronellol<br />\nCoumarin<br />\nIsoeugenol<br />\nAlpha Isomethyl Ionone<br />\nBenzyl Alcohol<br />\nHexyl Cinnamal<br />\nColour 42090 &lt;==色素<br />\nColour 17200<br />\nMethylparaben<br />\nPropylparaben<br />\n<br />\n排得越頭即係用量越多 <br />\n通常d標榜天然ge product, 香料係排好後面...</blockquote><br />\n色素只係平時個d食用食素 你平時食蛋糕個d<br />\nPerfume可以係解精油，通常呢個成份會係由植物天然精油同其他化學合成精油組成，唔會全部都係化學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以上既野只套用係lush"},{"pid":"1a9bb46f49ee8e6b93c2deaad80c70c7481902f7","tid":119380,"uid":58951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T11:09:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一齊買得唔得 <br />\n比你燒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nTg practicenow"},{"pid":"3414901503ba00a9b5353d2e8986f196e10c8b81","tid":119380,"uid":43518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T11:43:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一齊買得唔得 <br />\n比你燒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nTg practicenow</blockquote><br />\n有無紅色個隻肉桂洗頭皂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7941788ab58c692915ae01d6f2c70b52e0bb34","tid":119380,"uid":58951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T11:52:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一齊買得唔得 <br />\n比你燒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nTg practicenow</blockquote><br />\n有無紅色個隻肉桂洗頭皂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你上個網睇下<br />\n一樓有link"},{"pid":