ad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係可以解精油/精油成分<br />\n打粒星個d全部都係精油成分tim<br />\n但係佢只係精油提取出黎的成分<br />\n根本就係為加味而加入去的香料<br />\n真正的精油唔單止有味<br />\n亦有佢護膚上同埋心靈上的作用<br />\n而單單提取出黎的成分絕對無相同效果<br />\n單單薰衣草、玫瑰都有過百隻化合物<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一隻天然牌子走去用paraben?<br />\n點過ecocert<br />\n佢充其量只係一隻有添加過天然原料的護膚品牌<br />\n仲要d天然原料 好渣"},{"pid":"ce30490817c6d8c37b911b110f3fb669131a1eda","tid":119380,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T12:23:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Lush員工路過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得罪講句 間鋪極臭 你地點頂？</blockquote><br />\nagger<br />\n次次經過都抖唔到氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa74a78d80dd2172074952f490c8ea280771eff","tid":119380,"uid":57000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T12:25:31.000Z","msg":"洗髮皂有sls 唔係對頭髮唔好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3d33685ad9f3ac72359a003bf3db5461d87420","tid":119380,"uid":48266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T12:44:01.000Z","msg":"想夾 要買body spray &amp; 洗面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nTg: letmegoroses"},{"pid":"356aeac5b0c42e204c9513da22dac64954b5b7d5","tid":119380,"uid":75358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T13:05:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一齊買得唔得 <br />\n比你燒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nTg practicenow</blockquote><br />\n有無紅色個隻肉桂洗頭皂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用完無咩效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}